Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.32,0:00:24.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,《星際迷航: 新世界》前情提要\N{\rENG}Previously on Star Trek: Strange New Worlds...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.32,0:00:28.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,向在通訊範圍內的所有聯邦星艦求救\N{\rENG}To any Federation vessels in range, need help.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.34,0:00:30.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,遭遇戈恩人襲擊\N{\rENG}Under attack by the Gorn.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.14,0:00:34.30,CHS,,0,0,0,,如今星際聯邦和戈恩霸權的關係非常緊張\N{\rENG}The Federation's at a dangerous point in our relationship with the Gorn Hegemony.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.30,0:00:36.25,CHS,,0,0,0,,這看起來像是一條分界線\N{\rENG}It looks like a demarcation line.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.25,0:00:38.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,帕納索斯貝塔星和他們所有的武裝力量\N{\rENG}With Parnassus Beta and all their forces
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.04,0:00:39.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,在這條線的另一邊\N{\rENG}on the far side of the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.65,0:00:40.77,CHS,,0,0,0,,不幸的是 我認為我們的人\N{\rENG}Unfortunately, that is where
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.77,0:00:42.17,CHS,,0,0,0,,被關押在那裡\N{\rENG}I believe our people are being held.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.17,0:00:44.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,我不打算丟下他們不管\N{\rENG}I don't plan on leaving them behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.44,0:00:50.74,CHS,,0,0,0,,如果我頭腦裡藏著的東西是拯救進取號的答案\N{\rENG}If somewhere in my head is the answer to saving the Enterprise,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.74,0:00:51.87,CHS,,0,0,0,,那我必須冒這個險\N{\rENG}then that's a risk I have to take.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.04,0:00:52.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,拿著這個\N{\rENG}Take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.64,0:00:54.76,CHS,,0,0,0,,它能幫你藏起來\N{\rENG}It'll help you hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.24,0:00:57.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,快跑\N{\rENG}Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.88,0:00:59.84,CHS,,0,0,0,,在下蒙哥馬利·斯考特\N{\rENG}Montgomery Scott at your service.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.84,0:01:01.45,CHS,,0,0,0,,你怎麼還活著\N{\rENG}How are you not dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.45,0:01:03.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,我知道如何隱藏在眾目睽睽之下\N{\rENG}Well, I figured out how to hide in plain sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.56,0:01:05.54,CHS,,0,0,0,,你造了個戈恩人的應答器嗎\N{\rENG}You built a Gorn transponder?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.54,0:01:06.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,總的來說 對於掃描儀而言\N{\rENG}Eh, basically, to a scanner,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.94,0:01:08.63,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們的穿梭機看起來像是戈恩飛船\N{\rENG}the shuttle looked like a Gorn ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.63,0:01:10.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,你還能再造一個類似之前的設備嗎\N{\rENG}Could you build another device like the one you made?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.28,0:01:11.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,發生什麼了\N{\rENG}What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.98,0:01:14.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,巴特爾艦長需要馬上注射鎮定劑\N{\rENG}Captain Batel is in need of immediate sedation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.36,0:01:15.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,昨天發生的\N{\rENG}Happened yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.88,0:01:17.03,CHS,,0,0,0,,我不會放棄她的\N{\rENG}I'm not giving up on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.03,0:01:18.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,我也沒那個打算\N{\rENG}I have no intention of doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.34,0:01:21.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,艦長 傳送機目前在星球表面上未探測到任何人\N{\rENG}Captain, the transporter is not currently picking up anyone on the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.56,0:01:29.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,艾普里爾上將命令我們馬上撤離\N{\rENG}Admiral April's ordering our immediate withdrawal.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.14,0:01:31.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,殖民地居民和外勤隊\N{\rENG}The colonists and the landing party
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.26,0:01:33.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,顯然被傳送到了\N{\rENG}appear to have been beamed up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.06,0:01:33.92,CHS,,0,0,0,,戈恩人的船上\N{\rENG}by the Gorn.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.92,0:01:35.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,艦長 請下令\N{\rENG}Orders, Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.00,0:01:41.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,現在 即將揭曉結局\N{\rENG}And now, the conclusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.33,0:02:03.54,CHS,,0,0,0,,艦長 請下令\N{\rENG}Orders, Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.54,0:02:05.47,CHS,,0,0,0,,護盾只剩50%了\N{\rENG}Shields at 50%.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.60,0:02:07.99,CHS,,0,0,0,,艦長\N{\rENG}Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.26,0:02:13.43,CHS,,0,0,0,,艦長 請下令\N{\rENG}Orders, Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.80,0:02:15.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,烏乎拉 再重複一下上將剛剛的命令\N{\rENG}Uhura, repeat April's last order.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.82,0:02:16.73,CHS,,0,0,0,,撤退 並且\N{\rENG}Retreat and rendez...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.38,0:02:19.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,撤退並與艦隊匯合 艦長\N{\rENG}Retreat and rendezvous with the fleet, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.32,0:02:20.60,CHS,,0,0,0,,他給了坐標\N{\rENG}He gave coordinates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.60,0:02:21.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,但他沒說要立即會合 對吧\N{\rENG}But he didn't say immediately?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.42,0:02:25.50,CHS,,0,0,0,,行了 各位有什麼點子嗎\N{\rENG}All right, who's got ideas?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.50,0:02:26.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,聲東擊西\N{\rENG}Diversionary tactics.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.78,0:02:27.66,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們被圍困得太厲害了\N{\rENG}We're too boxed in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.66,0:02:29.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,排空曲速艙 製造一片等離子云團?\N{\rENG}Vent the nacelles, create a cloud?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.54,0:02:30.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,那我們自己也看不見了\N{\rENG}We need to be able to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.62,0:02:31.45,CHS,,0,0,0,,干擾敵方的通訊\N{\rENG}Jam their comms
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.45,0:02:32.93,CHS,,0,0,0,,使其無法協調攻擊\N{\rENG}so they can't coordinate attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.06,0:02:34.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,對 就是這個\N{\rENG}That's it. That's the one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.85,0:02:39.80,CHS,,0,0,0,,戈恩人使用光信號作為艦對艦通訊手段\N{\rENG}The Gorn use light for ship-to-ship messaging.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.50,0:02:42.92,CHS,,0,0,0,,我正在調整偏導陣列來發射光譜\N{\rENG}I'm modulating the deflector array to emit a spectrum.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.92,0:02:44.20,CHS,,0,0,0,,應該能迷惑他們一陣\N{\rENG}Should confuse them for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.47,0:02:49.99,CHS,,0,0,0,,好 現在想想要怎麼把自己人傳送回來\N{\rENG}All right, now how do we beam our people back to Enterprise?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.12,0:02:52.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,掃描顯示戈恩星艦能夠阻斷傳送\N{\rENG}Scans indicate the Gorn ships are transport-resistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.28,0:02:53.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,所以即便我們繞過了護盾\N{\rENG}So, even if we get past the shields,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.44,0:02:54.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,也需要授權碼才行\N{\rENG}we need authorization codes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.62,0:02:55.76,CHS,,0,0,0,,沒時間去破解密碼了\N{\rENG}No time to hack codes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.76,0:02:57.24,CHS,,0,0,0,,先撤再救\N{\rENG}Retreat and rescue.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.38,0:02:58.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,這是一堆爛選項裡最好的了\N{\rENG}It's the best of a bunch of bad options.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.94,0:03:00.40,CHS,,0,0,0,,那我們要怎樣追蹤一艘\N{\rENG}So how do we track this specific ship
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.40,0:03:01.83,CHS,,0,0,0,,跨越數光年的船呢\N{\rENG}across light-years of space?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.83,0:03:03.42,CHS,,0,0,0,,沃凱礦 一種稀有元素\N{\rENG}Wolkite. A rare element
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.42,0:03:05.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,含有子空間規範玻色子\N{\rENG}that contains subspace gauge bosons.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.22,0:03:06.66,CHS,,0,0,0,,如果我們調整一個定位信標\N{\rENG}If we modified a homing beacon...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.96,0:03:08.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,戈恩人遠遠地就能看到信標飛過來\N{\rENG}The Gorn would see a beacon coming from a mile away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.88,0:03:10.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,如果是魚雷就不會\N{\rENG}Not if it's a torpedo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.97,0:03:13.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們對他們發射一顆啞彈\N{\rENG}We tag 'em with a dud.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.18,0:03:14.42,CHS,,0,0,0,,戈恩人猜不到我們要幹什麼\N{\rENG}The Gorn won't know what we're up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.98,0:03:21.41,CHS,,0,0,0,,護盾只剩30%了\N{\rENG}Shields at 30%.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.41,0:03:23.22,CHS,,0,0,0,,要想這個方法奏效 我們仍需穿透\N{\rENG}For this to succeed, we still need to penetrate
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.22,0:03:24.48,CHS,,0,0,0,,戈恩星艦的護盾系統\N{\rENG}the Gorn's defensive systems.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.48,0:03:26.22,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們已經用上了所有武器攻擊他們\N{\rENG}We've been hitting them with everything we've got,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.22,0:03:27.07,CHS,,0,0,0,,沒多大用\N{\rENG}it doesn't do much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.07,0:03:29.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,能量護盾基於諧波運作\N{\rENG}Uh, energy shields work on harmonics.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.64,0:03:31.12,CHS,,0,0,0,,如果我們找對頻率\N{\rENG}If we find the right frequency...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.12,0:03:32.51,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們可以撞擊敵艦\N{\rENG}We can ram the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.84,0:03:33.60,CHS,,0,0,0,,確實\N{\rENG}Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.95,0:03:35.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們的護盾和他們的接觸時\N{\rENG}When our shields make contact with theirs,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.69,0:03:37.30,CHS,,0,0,0,,兩列諧波疊加時會出現相消干涉現象\N{\rENG}they will create a destructive interference pattern
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.43,0:03:39.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,並在短時間內中斷這兩個頻率的護盾\N{\rENG}and momentarily interrupt both frequencies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.39,0:03:42.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,沒有護盾 我們就是活靶子\N{\rENG}With our shields down, we'd be sitting ducks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.28,0:03:43.40,CHS,,0,0,0,,那我們就只有一次機會\N{\rENG}We'd only have one shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.40,0:03:44.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,這就足夠了\N{\rENG}That's all we need.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.04,0:03:45.22,CHS,,0,0,0,,米歇爾 調轉方向\N{\rENG}Mitchell, bring us around,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.22,0:03:46.60,CHS,,0,0,0,,與敵方驅逐艦正面交火\N{\rENG}head-to-head with the destroyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.79,0:03:49.40,CHS,,0,0,0,,是時候來點硬碰硬了\N{\rENG}Time to play a game of chicken.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.14,0:04:03.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,全艦注意 做好衝擊準備\N{\rENG}All decks, prepare for impact.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.72,0:04:05.46,CHS,,0,0,0,,隨時可讓脈衝引擎全速推進 艦長\N{\rENG}Full impulse on your orders, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.46,0:04:06.81,CHS,,0,0,0,,讓慣性阻尼器最大功率運行\N{\rENG}Inertial dampeners to maximum.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.98,0:04:08.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,所有人 抓穩扶好了\N{\rENG}Everybody hold onto something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.84,0:04:10.76,CHS,,0,0,0,,烏娜\N{\rENG}Una...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.14,0:04:12.92,CHS,,0,0,0,,動手吧\N{\rENG}let's hit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.05,0:04:29.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,發射魚雷\N{\rENG}Fire torpedoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.79,0:04:35.66,CHS,,0,0,0,,舵手 曲速帶離\N{\rENG}Helm, warp us out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.66,0:04:36.52,CHS,,0,0,0,,遵命\N{\rENG}On it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.12,0:04:38.49,CHS,,0,0,0,,堅持住 各位\N{\rENG}Hang in there, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.91,0:06:38.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,艦長 我們已到達會合點\N{\rENG}Captain, we've arrived at the rendezvous point.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.62,0:06:41.31,CHS,,0,0,0,,聯邦星艦巴勃羅·畢加索號在聯絡我們\N{\rENG}The USS Pablo Picasso is hailing to greet us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.62,0:06:43.02,CHS,,0,0,0,,是艾普里爾上將 艦長\N{\rENG}It's Admiral April, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.02,0:06:44.74,CHS,,0,0,0,,他現在要傳送上艦聽取匯報\N{\rENG}He's beaming aboard now to debrief.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.26,0:06:47.52,CHS,,0,0,0,,還要打針嗎\N{\rENG}More needles?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.52,0:06:48.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,沒錯 得再來幾針\N{\rENG}Yes, just a few more pokes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.32,0:06:50.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,沒有這些\N{\rENG}I mean, without these,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.28,0:06:53.50,CHS,,0,0,0,,你的身體會在靜滯場裡面壞死 所以\N{\rENG}your body will go necrotic in the stasis field, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.18,0:06:56.02,CHS,,0,0,0,,你會變紫 會很難看\N{\rENG}Things turn purple. It's not pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.56,0:06:58.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,我從沒被凍結冬眠過\N{\rENG}I've never been frozen solid before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.44,0:07:00.59,CHS,,0,0,0,,這前景不怎麼激動人心\N{\rENG}It's not an exciting prospect.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.59,0:07:03.77,CHS,,0,0,0,,沒事 等我們解決了這小小的戈恩卵感染問題\N{\rENG}Well, as soon as we work out this little Gorn infection,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.94,0:07:05.81,CHS,,0,0,0,,你就又能活蹦亂跳的了\N{\rENG}you'll be up and around again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.81,0:07:08.86,Note,,0,0,0,,* 原文是指小說《瑞普·凡·溫克爾》裡主人公一覺睡了二十年 醒來發現世界已經天翻地覆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.81,0:07:08.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,感覺我會像小說裡瑞普那樣 一醒來發現一切都變了\N{\rENG}So this could be like a Rip Van Winkle thing for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.95,0:07:11.43,CHS,,0,0,0,,我覺得你更會像是睡美人\N{\rENG}I see you more as a Sleeping Beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.62,0:07:15.91,CHS,,0,0,0,,聽著 我之前說的是認真的\N{\rENG}Listen, I meant what I said before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.32,0:07:18.17,CHS,,0,0,0,,一旦那時要在我和其他船員之間做出選擇\N{\rENG}The moment it looks like me or the crew,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.17,0:07:19.22,CHS,,0,0,0,,就犧牲掉我\N{\rENG}you take me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.96,0:07:21.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,不要想這些了\N{\rENG}Don't think about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.66,0:07:24.53,CHS,,0,0,0,,靜滯狀態會阻止你和戈恩胚胎\N{\rENG}Stasis will prevent you and the Gorn
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.53,0:07:26.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,進行任何形式的細胞生長\N{\rENG}from any type of cellular growth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.82,0:07:28.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,做好最壞的打算\N{\rENG}There's another side to the coin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.10,0:07:32.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,無論代價如何\N{\rENG}Whatever it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.22,0:07:37.41,CHS,,0,0,0,,無論代價如何 我保證\N{\rENG}Whatever it takes. I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.48,0:07:41.19,CHS,,0,0,0,,我現在要給你注射鎮靜劑了\N{\rENG}I'm, uh, I'm gonna give you a sedative now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.37,0:07:44.33,CHS,,0,0,0,,等你醒來 戈恩感染的問題就治好了\N{\rENG}And when you wake up, you will be Gorn-free.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.39,0:08:04.09,CHS,,0,0,0,,腎上腺素和中和劑 快\N{\rENG}Epinephrine and neutralizer, stat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.57,0:08:07.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,她的身體正在排斥血清\N{\rENG}Her body's rejecting the serum.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.57,0:08:14.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,醫務室呼叫艦橋\N{\rENG}Sickbay to bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.00,0:08:16.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,有個最新消息 情況不太樂觀\N{\rENG}Uh, I have an update, and it's not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.62,0:08:17.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,告訴我最壞情況\N{\rENG}Bottom line it for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.89,0:08:20.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,巴特爾艦長對低溫血清過敏\N{\rENG}Captain Batel is allergic to cryoserum.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.68,0:08:23.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們不能把她放進靜滯狀態\N{\rENG}We can't put her in stasis.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.74,0:08:25.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,那她的生命已經進入倒計時了嗎\N{\rENG}So she's back on a ticking clock?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.84,0:08:29.22,CHS,,0,0,0,,她身體裡的戈恩卵會在\N{\rENG}The Gorn will hatch from her body in, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.33,0:08:30.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,一天之內孵化\N{\rENG}in less than a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.86,0:08:35.51,CHS,,0,0,0,,我正在努力尋找治療的方法\N{\rENG}I'm stuck trying to find a treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.51,0:08:38.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,但是\N{\rENG}Um... uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.16,0:08:40.33,CHS,,0,0,0,,也許如果約瑟夫在這裡 就可以\N{\rENG}maybe if Joseph was here, I could...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.84,0:08:44.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,我會派人去幫忙\N{\rENG}I'm sending help.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.44,0:08:45.80,CHS,,0,0,0,,克莉絲汀\N{\rENG}Christine...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.00,0:08:49.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,我相信你\N{\rENG}I believe in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.12,0:08:51.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,救救她\N{\rENG}Help her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.74,0:08:53.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,我會盡我所能 艦長\N{\rENG}I'll do my best, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.05,0:08:57.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,艦長 我或許不是醫生\N{\rENG}Captain, I may not be a doctor,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.58,0:08:59.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,但我能夠把我所有的能力都奉獻在巴特爾艦長的治療上\N{\rENG}but I will dedicate all of my abilities to Captain Batel
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.90,0:09:03.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,直到解決她的戈恩卵感染\N{\rENG}until her Gorn infection is... resolved.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.50,0:09:13.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,就只是看著?\N{\rENG}Just stand by?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.54,0:09:16.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,你可是有一整支艦隊在待命啊\N{\rENG}You have the entire fleet out there ready to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.72,0:09:18.47,CHS,,0,0,0,,這是力量展示\N{\rENG}It's a show of force.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.64,0:09:20.40,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們先要建立起有效的巡邏\N{\rENG}First we need to establish patrols.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.40,0:09:22.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,他們真這麼覺得嗎\N{\rENG}Do they really think
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.82,0:09:24.96,CHS,,0,0,0,,覺得戈恩人只要炸完這些殖民地\N{\rENG}the Gorn are just gonna stop and go home
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.96,0:09:26.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,就會收手然後回家?\N{\rENG}after they raided those colonies?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.96,0:09:28.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,好吧 這是很棘手的情況\N{\rENG}Look, it's a tough situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.88,0:09:30.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,但我們必須一次解決一個問題\N{\rENG}but we have to manage it one piece at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.64,0:09:32.40,CHS,,0,0,0,,無數無辜生命正危在旦夕 鮑勃\N{\rENG}There are innocent lives at stake, Bob.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.40,0:09:33.31,CHS,,0,0,0,,我明白\N{\rENG}And I get that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.31,0:09:35.52,CHS,,0,0,0,,但這件事發生在我們的管轄範圍之外\N{\rENG}But it's happening outside of our jurisdiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.52,0:09:37.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,拜託 鮑勃\N{\rENG}Oh, come on, Bob.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.08,0:09:38.52,CHS,,0,0,0,,除了你那不怕死的狗斗之外\N{\rENG}Apart from your reckless dogfight,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.52,0:09:40.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,這些攻擊和聯邦並沒有關係\N{\rENG}these attacks do not involve the Federation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.32,0:09:42.48,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們有規定的 克里斯\N{\rENG}We have regulations, Chris.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.48,0:09:44.23,CHS,,0,0,0,,所以 就因為死的不是聯邦公民\N{\rENG}So, because it's non-Federation citizens that are dying,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.23,0:09:45.20,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們就作壁上觀嗎\N{\rENG}we do nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.20,0:09:47.02,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們對於聯邦成員國都有義務在身\N{\rENG}We have an obligation to our member worlds.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.02,0:09:48.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,那可是數十億人\N{\rENG}Billions of lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.94,0:09:50.40,CHS,,0,0,0,,現在就貿然投入戰爭\N{\rENG}To rush into a fight right now
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.40,0:09:51.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,會將所有人都置於危險當中\N{\rENG}puts all of them at risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.16,0:09:52.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們不能這樣\N{\rENG}We can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.06,0:09:53.46,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們還沒從克林貢戰爭中完全恢復\N{\rENG}We're still recovering from the Klingon War.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.46,0:09:55.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,你說得一點沒錯\N{\rENG}You are absolutely right,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.04,0:09:57.02,CHS,,0,0,0,,戈恩就是利用這一點發動進攻\N{\rENG}and the Gorn sense our weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.74,0:09:58.76,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們現在是獵物\N{\rENG}We are prey.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.32,0:10:05.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,他們只會把這條霸權的邊境線\N{\rENG}They will push this Hegemony line
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.32,0:10:07.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,向著聯邦領空內部推得越來越深\N{\rENG}further and further into Federation space.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.64,0:10:08.73,CHS,,0,0,0,,你也知道他們會這麼做\N{\rENG}And you know they will.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.73,0:10:09.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,等到我們真的恢復過來\N{\rENG}And by the time we actually get around
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.98,0:10:11.22,CHS,,0,0,0,,有精力反制的時候\N{\rENG}to doing something about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.78,0:10:13.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,一切就太晚了\N{\rENG}it'll be way too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.70,0:10:19.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,我聽說了外勤隊的事\N{\rENG}I heard about the landing party.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.22,0:10:20.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,對啊 還有幾百號殖民地居民呢\N{\rENG}Yeah, and a couple hundred colonists, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.76,0:10:23.92,CHS,,0,0,0,,瑪麗呢\N{\rENG}And Marie?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.84,0:10:28.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,她在醫務室裡\N{\rENG}She's in sickbay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.64,0:10:39.96,CHS,,0,0,0,,官方地說 給你的命令是監控分界線\N{\rENG}Officially, your orders are to monitor the demarcation line
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.96,0:10:41.48,CHS,,0,0,0,,避免戈恩人的進一步進犯\N{\rENG}for any encroachment by the Gorn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.66,0:10:49.21,CHS,,0,0,0,,好 那不官方的呢\N{\rENG}Okay. And unofficially?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.43,0:10:55.91,CHS,,0,0,0,,為何不給他們點顏色看看 告訴他們我們不是獵物\N{\rENG}How do we punch back and show them we aren't prey?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.60,0:10:59.74,CHS,,0,0,0,,行 我接受這個\N{\rENG}Yeah, I can do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.74,0:11:01.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,你做的這個裝置\N{\rENG}This contraption of yours,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.34,0:11:02.92,CHS,,0,0,0,,你再說一遍它是幹什麼的\N{\rENG}what's it supposed to do again?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.92,0:11:05.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,發射極化電磁信號\N{\rENG}Emit a polarized EM signature that
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.26,0:11:07.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,誘騙戈恩 讓它們以為我們是他們中的一員\N{\rENG}tricks the Gorn into thinking we're one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.28,0:11:08.71,CHS,,0,0,0,,類似隱身裝置的原理\N{\rENG}It's like a cloaking device.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.71,0:11:10.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,那麼它究竟是怎麼做到這一點的\N{\rENG}And how, exactly, does it do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.34,0:11:12.74,CHS,,0,0,0,,說實話 我不太記得了\N{\rENG}Ah, if I'm being honest, I don't really remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.74,0:11:14.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,我就是當時靈機一動\N{\rENG}I was kind of in the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.00,0:11:16.11,CHS,,0,0,0,,很好 那我現在要問一個很蠢的問題\N{\rENG}Well, now I'm going to ask a silly question,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.11,0:11:18.24,CHS,,0,0,0,,而且我確定我知道答案\N{\rENG}to which I'm pretty sure I know the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.68,0:11:20.11,CHS,,0,0,0,,別又來這個\N{\rENG}Not this again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.11,0:11:21.63,CHS,,0,0,0,,就像回到了報告廳一樣\N{\rENG}It's like being back in lecture hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.63,0:11:23.50,CHS,,0,0,0,,你怎麼知道 你又沒去過報告廳\N{\rENG}How would you know that? You were never there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.50,0:11:25.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,我去過 在後排而已\N{\rENG}I was there, in the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.18,0:11:27.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,你在把這堆東西拼起來時\N{\rENG}Did you record a work-in-progress log
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.34,0:11:28.96,CHS,,0,0,0,,有沒有記工作日誌\N{\rENG}while you were jury-rigging this up?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.96,0:11:31.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,啥 您的意思是在戈恩人正在轟炸我的時候記錄?\N{\rENG}What, you mean as the Gorn were tearing our ship apart?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.56,0:11:34.50,CHS,,0,0,0,,斯考特 工程學第一定律就是寫下來\N{\rENG}First rule in engineering, Scotty: write it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.50,0:11:36.43,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們被要求無論什麼情況下\N{\rENG}There's a reason we track our work
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.43,0:11:38.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,都要記錄自己的工作是有理由的\N{\rENG}no matter what the circumstance, and this,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.78,0:11:41.91,CHS,,0,0,0,,現在的這個情況 就是最好的理由\N{\rENG}this right now, this is precisely the reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.91,0:11:43.83,CHS,,0,0,0,,抱歉打斷\N{\rENG}Pardon the interruption.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.24,0:11:45.40,CHS,,0,0,0,,你們還要多久能讓這東西恢復運作\N{\rENG}How long before you get that working?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.53,0:11:46.92,CHS,,0,0,0,,哦 派克艦長 問題是\N{\rENG}Oh, Captain Pike, the thing is,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.01,0:11:48.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,它在我的小穿梭機上能起作用\N{\rENG}it worked on my wee shuttle,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.56,0:11:49.22,CHS,,0,0,0,,但進取號就\N{\rENG}but the Enterprise is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.22,0:11:51.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,那您什麼時候需要它呢 艦長\N{\rENG}How soon do you need it, Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.16,0:11:52.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們正在航向戈恩的領空\N{\rENG}We're headed into Gorn space,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.64,0:11:53.50,CHS,,0,0,0,,所以現在能用就最好了\N{\rENG}so now would be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.50,0:11:56.84,CHS,,0,0,0,,在我們跨過分界線之前它會準備好的\N{\rENG}It'll be up and working before we cross the Hegemony line.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.97,0:11:59.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,我希望如此 因為我和船上所有人的命都指望在它身上了\N{\rENG}I'm counting on it, as are the lives of everyone on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.58,0:12:00.63,CHS,,0,0,0,,不管有沒有這個裝置\N{\rENG}We're going after our missing crew,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.63,0:12:01.76,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們都要去搜救被抓走的船員\N{\rENG}with or without that device.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.15,0:12:04.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,明白了嗎\N{\rENG}Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.32,0:12:07.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,哇 還真是一點壓力都沒有呢\N{\rENG}Well, that's no pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.23,0:12:36.12,CHS,,0,0,0,,媽媽\N{\rENG}Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.12,0:12:37.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,拉安 勇敢點\N{\rENG}La'An, be brave.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.92,0:12:41.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,對危險沒有畏懼之心才會置你於死地\N{\rENG}Not believing you're gonna die is what gets you killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.41,0:12:43.15,CHS,,0,0,0,,那是戈恩人\N{\rENG}It's the Gorn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.15,0:12:44.50,CHS,,0,0,0,,醒醒\N{\rENG}Wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.63,0:12:45.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,快醒醒\N{\rENG}Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.02,0:13:32.42,CHS,,0,0,0,,你能做到的\N{\rENG}You can do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.56,0:13:36.30,CHS,,0,0,0,,第一個倒霉的總是醫生\N{\rENG}Always start with the doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.12,0:14:07.02,CHS,,0,0,0,,好了\N{\rENG}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.72,0:14:20.96,CHS,,0,0,0,,我的媽 我的手\N{\rENG}Holy crap, my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.94,0:14:23.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,我他媽的半隻手都沒了\N{\rENG}Half my hand is frickin' gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.44,0:14:25.22,CHS,,0,0,0,,艾麗卡 看著我\N{\rENG}Erica, look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.22,0:14:26.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,看著我 冷靜下來\N{\rENG}Look at me. Relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.44,0:14:31.39,CHS,,0,0,0,,會沒事的\N{\rENG}It's going to be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.43,0:14:36.35,CHS,,0,0,0,,只要我們能回到船上就能治好它\N{\rENG}We can fix this when we get back to the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.35,0:14:37.40,CHS,,0,0,0,,拜託\N{\rENG}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.09,0:14:40.54,CHS,,0,0,0,,先保持冷靜\N{\rENG}Try to stay calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.54,0:14:41.40,CHS,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\rENG}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.92,0:14:46.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,但怎麼\N{\rENG}How?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.58,0:14:51.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們怎麼才能回到船上\N{\rENG}How do we get back to the ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.68,0:14:54.89,CHS,,0,0,0,,而且他們怎麼辦\N{\rENG}What about them?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.72,0:14:58.30,CHS,,0,0,0,,如果我們一次只能解救一個人\N{\rENG}If we free them one at a time,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.40,0:15:01.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,那我們能救出來的人屈指可數\N{\rENG}we'll only get a handful out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.04,0:15:03.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,如果能的話\N{\rENG}If that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.36,0:15:06.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,光是我們四個人脫困就花了這麼久\N{\rENG}Look how long it took for the four of us to get loose.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.60,0:15:11.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,這是一個巨大的消化腔\N{\rENG}This is a massive digestive chamber.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.47,0:15:14.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,而且它正在消化\N{\rENG}And it's working its way through...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.38,0:15:16.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,看起來像是燃料加工廠\N{\rENG}looks like a-a processing plant for fuel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.78,0:15:18.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,或者只是戈恩人的食物工廠\N{\rENG}Or just food for the Gorn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.62,0:15:20.92,CHS,,0,0,0,,我真的不想變成哪個戈恩人的盤中餐\N{\rENG}I don't like the idea of being anyone's lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.44,0:15:23.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,即便我們能夠喚醒他們\N{\rENG}And even if we can wake them up,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.78,0:15:27.83,CHS,,0,0,0,,不管是一個還是一百個\N{\rENG}one or a hundred,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.97,0:15:31.23,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們還是沒法離開這個\N{\rENG}we still don't have a way out of...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.40,0:15:33.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,不知道什麼的地方\N{\rENG}wherever this is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.23,0:15:34.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,先一步一步來吧\N{\rENG}One step at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.26,0:15:37.24,CHS,,0,0,0,,要是什麼都不做 就是等死\N{\rENG}Sitting here doing nothing is a death sentence.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.37,0:15:38.20,CHS,,0,0,0,,而且搞不好\N{\rENG}And for all we know,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.20,0:15:40.67,CHS,,0,0,0,,那些戈恩人可能在我們醒來那會就被驚動了\N{\rENG}the Gorn were alerted the moment that we woke up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.85,0:15:42.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,所以那些殺人蜥蜴可能已經在來的路上了\N{\rENG}So the killer lizards could already be on their way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.58,0:15:43.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,他們來了\N{\rENG}They're coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.32,0:15:44.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,別害怕\N{\rENG}Don't be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.42,0:15:45.46,CHS,,0,0,0,,拉安\N{\rENG}La'An.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.59,0:15:46.85,CHS,,0,0,0,,無論發生什麼\N{\rENG}No matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.72,0:15:48.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,拉安\N{\rENG}La'An.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.64,0:15:52.47,CHS,,0,0,0,,上尉 你在想什麼\N{\rENG}What's on your mind, Lieutenant?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.17,0:15:57.52,CHS,,0,0,0,,你說得對\N{\rENG}You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.69,0:15:59.65,CHS,,0,0,0,,不僅僅關乎我們自己\N{\rENG}It's not just about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.06,0:16:02.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,這些殖民地居民很快也會被殺害\N{\rENG}All of these people will be dead soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.88,0:16:03.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,看這\N{\rENG}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.78,0:16:05.74,CHS,,0,0,0,,這看起來像個排泄樁\N{\rENG}This looks like an evacuation pile.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.87,0:16:10.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,也許 這艘船不能處理的東西 都由它排出\N{\rENG}Maybe whatever the ship can't process, it expels.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.89,0:16:26.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,糞堆裡的武器\N{\rENG}Weapons from a crap pile.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.76,0:16:33.29,CHS,,0,0,0,,怪了 這個方向是對的\N{\rENG}Strangely, it's a step in the right direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.62,0:16:37.43,CHS,,0,0,0,,我不想只救下屈指可數的人\N{\rENG}I don't want to save a handful of colonists,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.43,0:16:38.99,CHS,,0,0,0,,我想拯救全部人\N{\rENG}I want to save them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.17,0:16:41.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,所有還活著的人 都能回家\N{\rENG}Everyone that's still alive gets home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.74,0:16:46.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,即使這意味著 我們必須殺出一條血路\N{\rENG}Even if we have to shoot our way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.98,0:17:12.84,CHS,,0,0,0,,哎呀 你個蠢貨\N{\rENG}Ack, bawheid.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.96,0:17:14.92,CHS,,0,0,0,,不是這樣\N{\rENG}That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.92,0:17:16.42,CHS,,0,0,0,,是戈恩人 他們來了\N{\rENG}They're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.51,0:17:17.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,該死\N{\rENG}Oh, shite.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.64,0:17:19.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們完蛋了 斯考提\N{\rENG}We're doomed. Scotty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.34,0:17:19.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,不不不不\N{\rENG}No, no, no, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.94,0:17:21.22,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們都死定了\N{\rENG}We're all gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.74,0:17:25.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,成功了\N{\rENG}It's working.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.00,0:17:26.48,CHS,,0,0,0,,快通知艦橋 把它加到護盾上\N{\rENG}Tell the bridge to patch it to the shields.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.18,0:17:29.55,CHS,,0,0,0,,怎麼 太晚了嗎\N{\rENG}What? Is it too late?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.55,0:17:31.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,艦橋呼叫科學實驗室 你們進展如何了\N{\rENG}Bridge to science lab. What's the status down there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.32,0:17:32.80,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們馬上要進入戈恩領空了\N{\rENG}We're about to enter Gorn space.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.80,0:17:34.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,真是狡猾\N{\rENG}Oh, you minx.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.38,0:17:35.75,CHS,,0,0,0,,已經在正常運行了 艦長\N{\rENG}It's up and running, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.75,0:17:38.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們現在就能把它加到護盾上\N{\rENG}We can patch it into the shields now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.28,0:17:39.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,好極了 派克完畢\N{\rENG}Excellent. Pike out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.28,0:17:40.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,一點都不好笑\N{\rENG}That wasn't funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.28,0:17:41.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,明明就很有趣\N{\rENG}It was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.28,0:17:42.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,你差點害我心臟病發作\N{\rENG}You nearly gave me a heart attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.56,0:17:44.49,CHS,,0,0,0,,我那麼做 是因為我了解你\N{\rENG}I did it 'cause I know you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.49,0:17:45.74,CHS,,0,0,0,,你才不了解呢\N{\rENG}No, you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.74,0:17:48.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,太了解了 平時閒得發慌的時候你就擺了\N{\rENG}Yes, with too much time on your hands, you fall apart,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.16,0:17:50.24,CHS,,0,0,0,,但要是有相位槍頂著你的頭 你立刻精神百倍\N{\rENG}but put a phaser to your head and voilà.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.24,0:17:52.24,CHS,,0,0,0,,你管我這麼多幹嘛\N{\rENG}Why do you care what I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.98,0:17:55.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,你防備太重了 斯考提\N{\rENG}You put up walls, Scotty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.16,0:17:56.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,你太害怕承擔風險了\N{\rENG}You're too afraid to take a risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.78,0:17:58.84,CHS,,0,0,0,,我修好了你想讓我修的東西\N{\rENG}I fixed what you wanted me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.84,0:18:00.52,CHS,,0,0,0,,而且你相當目無上級\N{\rENG}And you're insubordinate to boot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.52,0:18:02.42,CHS,,0,0,0,,準確來說你又不是我的上級\N{\rENG}Well, technically you're not my C.O.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.42,0:18:03.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,她在馭星號上犧牲了\N{\rENG}She went down on the Stardiver.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.32,0:18:07.47,CHS,,0,0,0,,我可以離開了嗎 長官\N{\rENG}May I be excused, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.47,0:18:08.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,哦 斯考提\N{\rENG}Oh, Scotty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.80,0:18:20.27,CHS,,0,0,0,,艦長 我們正在接近戈恩霸權領空邊境\N{\rENG}Approaching the Hegemony demarcation line now, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.86,0:18:21.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,脫離曲速\N{\rENG}Drop us out of warp.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.78,0:18:23.24,CHS,,0,0,0,,開啟斯考特的應答器\N{\rENG}Start Mr. Scott's transponder.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.24,0:18:24.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,應答器?\N{\rENG}Transponder?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.14,0:18:26.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,佩利亞說它更像是一個改裝過的電磁脈衝發射器\N{\rENG}Pelia says it's more like a modified EM pulse emitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.72,0:18:28.33,CHS,,0,0,0,,好吧 那就說得通了\N{\rENG}Okay, then that makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.52,0:18:31.50,CHS,,0,0,0,,戈恩人肯定不使用光學數據\N{\rENG}The Gorn must not use optical data.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.63,0:18:33.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,他們已經進化了\N{\rENG}They've evolved,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.08,0:18:35.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,所以他們一定依賴生物識別信息\N{\rENG}so they must rely on biometrics,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.38,0:18:37.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,熱量和電磁信號\N{\rENG}heat and EM signatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.62,0:18:39.85,CHS,,0,0,0,,嗯 是時候看看這到底能不能成功了\N{\rENG}Well, time to see if it actually works.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.85,0:18:41.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,我的意思是 它應該可以\N{\rENG}It should. I mean,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.50,0:18:44.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,除非哪個戈恩人突然決定看一眼窗外\N{\rENG}unless maybe one of them decides to look out a window.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.73,0:18:48.69,CHS,,0,0,0,,艦長 戈恩狩獵艦正在接近\N{\rENG}Captain, Gorn hunters approaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.74,0:18:54.43,CHS,,0,0,0,,保持穩定航線\N{\rENG}Keep us steady and on course.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.92,0:19:01.68,CHS,,0,0,0,,目前為止 我沒看到任何窗戶\N{\rENG}So far, I don't see any windows.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.26,0:19:17.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,它奏效了\N{\rENG}It worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.40,0:19:20.37,CHS,,0,0,0,,烏乎拉 我們還能接收到沃凱礦信標的信號嗎\N{\rENG}Uhura, do we still have a signal from the wolkite beacon?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.50,0:19:21.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,是的 艦長\N{\rENG}Aye, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.07,0:19:24.54,CHS,,0,0,0,,信號很弱且在逐漸減弱 但它還在發射信號\N{\rENG}It's faint and getting weaker but still there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.62,0:19:26.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,有關於他們去向的情報嗎\N{\rENG}Any intel on where they're headed?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.16,0:19:28.50,CHS,,0,0,0,,一個未知的雙星系統\N{\rENG}An uncharted binary star system.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.50,0:19:30.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,那裡的恆星活動\N{\rENG}The stellar activity there
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.36,0:19:33.25,CHS,,0,0,0,,是我們前所未見的\N{\rENG}is like nothing we've ever seen before.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.25,0:19:34.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,舵手 設置航線\N{\rENG}Helm, plot a course.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.34,0:19:36.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,艦長 那個星系的輻射高得超出量表\N{\rENG}Captain, the radiation in that system is off the charts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.70,0:19:38.40,CHS,,0,0,0,,到最後 我們只能使用脈衝引擎\N{\rENG}At a certain point, we can only use impulse engines,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.40,0:19:40.48,CHS,,0,0,0,,進取號的護盾也無法抵擋輻射了\N{\rENG}and our shields won't be able to protect us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.48,0:19:41.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,了解 那我們快速行動\N{\rENG}Understood. We'll make it quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.72,0:19:43.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,米歇爾 曲速七級\N{\rENG}Mitchell, warp factor seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.00,0:19:44.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,遵命 艦長\N{\rENG}Aye aye, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.06,0:19:54.41,CHS,,0,0,0,,有趣\N{\rENG}Intriguing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.41,0:19:56.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,戈恩卵的孵化進程大幅改變了她身體的生物化學結構\N{\rENG}The incubation has severely altered her biochemistry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.97,0:19:58.96,CHS,,0,0,0,,她的身體現在依賴於戈恩的幼體\N{\rENG}Her body is now as dependent
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.04,0:20:01.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,就像戈恩幼體依賴於她\N{\rENG}on the Gorn hatchlings as they are on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.20,0:20:04.76,CHS,,0,0,0,,完美的宿主 不可分割\N{\rENG}The perfect host, inseparable.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.89,0:20:06.46,CHS,,0,0,0,,你試過顯微減瘤術了嗎\N{\rENG}Have you tried microscopic debulking?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.59,0:20:07.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,模擬完畢\N{\rENG}Results completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.16,0:20:10.55,CHS,,0,0,0,,這是我最後跑的一次模擬\N{\rENG}It's the last simulation I ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.55,0:20:13.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,死亡率為100%\N{\rENG}Probability of fatality is 100%.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.86,0:20:16.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,我做的每一次模擬 結果全都一樣\N{\rENG}That's the chorus of the day. It's every simulation I've run.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.43,0:20:20.95,CHS,,0,0,0,,計算機 模擬顯微減瘤術的情境\N{\rENG}Computer, run scenarios for microscopic debulking
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.95,0:20:23.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,將注射扎多拉提取物納入模擬變量中\N{\rENG}factoring for an infusion of Zadora extract.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.43,0:20:24.42,CHS,,0,0,0,,正在處理\N{\rENG}Processing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.68,0:20:26.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,獵戶星的街頭毒品?\N{\rENG}An Orion street drug?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.44,0:20:30.83,CHS,,0,0,0,,實話說 這真是天才想法\N{\rENG}Actually, that's kind of brilliant.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.92,0:20:34.20,CHS,,0,0,0,,是你教會了我跳出框架去看\N{\rENG}You are the one who taught me to look outside of the box.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.98,0:20:36.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,是「去思考」\N{\rENG}It's "think,"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.28,0:20:37.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,但也差不多\N{\rENG}but close enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.14,0:20:40.19,CHS,,0,0,0,,克莉絲汀\N{\rENG}Christine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.44,0:20:43.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,我知道你想談談\N{\rENG}I know you want to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.56,0:20:44.52,CHS,,0,0,0,,我會盡量簡短\N{\rENG}I will be brief.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.72,0:20:46.07,CHS,,0,0,0,,我只是想為你離開前\N{\rENG}I simply want to apologize
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.07,0:20:47.59,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們之間的結局道個歉\N{\rENG}for the way things ended before you left.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.58,0:20:50.29,CHS,,0,0,0,,我當時情緒有點失控\N{\rENG}I reacted poorly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.00,0:20:52.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,好了\N{\rENG}Apology accepted.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.86,0:20:54.07,CHS,,0,0,0,,原諒你了\N{\rENG}We're good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.40,0:20:56.95,CHS,,0,0,0,,失去你的念頭\N{\rENG}The thought of losing you,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.95,0:20:58.95,CHS,,0,0,0,,深深困擾著我\N{\rENG}it affected me deeply.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.34,0:21:00.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,我理解\N{\rENG}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.78,0:21:04.66,CHS,,0,0,0,,事情變得複雜了\N{\rENG}This has gotten complicated,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.66,0:21:06.22,CHS,,0,0,0,,我不擅長應對複雜\N{\rENG}and I am not good at complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.64,0:21:11.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,而我還是要離開三個月\N{\rENG}And I am still going away for three months
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.00,0:21:13.01,CHS,,0,0,0,,去和羅傑·科爾比一起學習\N{\rENG}to study with Roger Korby.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.86,0:21:16.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,等我回來 再看看我們的狀態吧\N{\rENG}When I get back, let's just see where we are then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.06,0:21:18.49,CHS,,0,0,0,,所以你是想說\N{\rENG}So you are saying that perhaps
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.49,0:21:20.01,CHS,,0,0,0,,也許分開一段時間 對我們有好處嗎\N{\rENG}some time apart might be good for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.00,0:21:22.41,CHS,,0,0,0,,史波克\N{\rENG}Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.89,0:21:25.42,CHS,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\rENG}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.56,0:21:28.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,但不是說\N{\rENG}But not like...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.98,0:21:32.55,CHS,,0,0,0,,作為我們倆的我們\N{\rENG}not like "us" us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.64,0:21:35.59,CHS,,0,0,0,,只是說\N{\rENG}Like...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.68,0:21:37.77,CHS,,0,0,0,,作為兩個個體的我們\N{\rENG}us as people.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.99,0:21:41.21,CHS,,0,0,0,,請別做那些你覺得浪漫的事\N{\rENG}Please don't do something you think is romantic,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.21,0:21:44.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,像是等我之類的\N{\rENG}like wait for me or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.76,0:21:47.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,扎多拉提取物情境模擬完畢\N{\rENG}Zadora extract scenario completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.14,0:21:50.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,死亡率為100%\N{\rENG}Probability of fatality is 100%.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.22,0:21:54.87,CHS,,0,0,0,,無論我們用什麼方法\N{\rENG}No matter how we approach this,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.87,0:21:56.96,CHS,,0,0,0,,巴特爾的人類基因\N{\rENG}Batel's human DNA is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.96,0:21:58.31,CHS,,0,0,0,,都存在不足\N{\rENG}Inadequate.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.62,0:22:01.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,她的身體進入休克狀態\N{\rENG}Her body goes into shock,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.44,0:22:02.46,CHS,,0,0,0,,血壓開始下降\N{\rENG}blood pressure drops.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.46,0:22:03.40,CHS,,0,0,0,,最後死亡\N{\rENG}And she dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.34,0:22:09.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,哼 人類的身體始終有限\N{\rENG}Huh. Human physiology.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.32,0:22:10.80,CHS,,0,0,0,,但如果我們給她的基因幫點忙呢\N{\rENG}What if we gave her some help there?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.93,0:22:12.20,CHS,,0,0,0,,你已經有主意了\N{\rENG}You have an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.54,0:22:13.81,CHS,,0,0,0,,伊勒利亞人的基因\N{\rENG}Illyrian DNA.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.66,0:22:15.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,烏娜的血液\N{\rENG}Una's blood,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.26,0:22:16.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,基因使其可以實時抵抗感染\N{\rENG}it's designed to combat infections in real time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.88,0:22:19.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,一劑血清可以給巴特爾的免疫系統來一次大升級\N{\rENG}A plasma injection could provide a boost to Batel's immunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.44,0:22:20.55,CHS,,0,0,0,,這樣我們就能在不使其休克的前提下\N{\rENG}And we could attempt the surgery
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.55,0:22:21.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,嘗試進行手術了\N{\rENG}without her going into shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.50,0:22:23.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,這樣做違反規定\N{\rENG}It is against regulation,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.90,0:22:25.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,但能挽救她的生命\N{\rENG}but it could save her life.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.90,0:22:28.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,計算機 模擬手術結果\N{\rENG}Computer, run scenario for surgery
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.04,0:22:31.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,將注射伊勒利亞血清納入模擬變量中\N{\rENG}factoring for a plasma transfusion from an Illyrian blood donor.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.70,0:22:33.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,處理中\N{\rENG}Processing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.09,0:22:35.39,CHS,,0,0,0,,你當時是怎麼說的來著\N{\rENG}How did you put it once?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.98,0:22:37.83,CHS,,0,0,0,,有些規則就是用來打破的?\N{\rENG}Some rules are intended to be broken?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.57,0:22:42.09,CHS,,0,0,0,,幾乎準確無誤了\N{\rENG}Almost exactly it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.52,0:22:43.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,這就是機庫\N{\rENG}There's the hangar.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.82,0:22:44.84,CHS,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\rENG}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.68,0:22:47.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,大家都了解計劃吧\N{\rENG}Everyone's clear on the plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.14,0:22:48.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,訪問這艘船的計算機主機\N{\rENG}Access the ship's mainframe,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.70,0:22:50.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,上傳戈恩星艦的傳送器密碼\N{\rENG}upload the Gorn transporter codes...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.38,0:22:52.19,CHS,,0,0,0,,把他們帶回進取號\N{\rENG}Get them to the Enterprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.19,0:22:54.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,要成功 我們必須偷一艘飛船 從這裡飛出去\N{\rENG}To do that, we have to steal a ship and fly it out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.82,0:22:56.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,這個看起來沒什麼警戒措施\N{\rENG}That one doesn't look guarded.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.44,0:22:59.46,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們超有把握 一點都不是不可能任務\N{\rENG}Totally got this, not impossible at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.03,0:23:02.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,你什麼都能飛 是真的吧\N{\rENG}And it's true you can fly anything, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.94,0:23:04.68,CHS,,0,0,0,,別這麼沒禮貌 當然是真的\N{\rENG}Don't be rude. Of course I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.50,0:23:07.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,好\N{\rENG}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.00,0:23:08.43,CHS,,0,0,0,,來搞定那艘飛船吧\N{\rENG}Let's get to that ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.76,0:23:11.69,CHS,,0,0,0,,這是個好計劃\N{\rENG}This is a good plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.44,0:23:13.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,一定行得通\N{\rENG}It's gonna work.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.78,0:23:19.13,CHS,,0,0,0,,這是個好計劃\N{\rENG}It's good. It's-it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.13,0:23:20.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,是個好計劃 對嗎\N{\rENG}It's a good plan, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.88,0:23:22.35,CHS,,0,0,0,,當然了\N{\rENG}It's a good plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.48,0:23:25.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,沒錯 我們現在只需要\N{\rENG}Yeah. Yeah. Now all we have to do is
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.31,0:23:27.27,CHS,,0,0,0,,別被戈恩人逮住\N{\rENG}not get caught by the Gorn.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.92,0:23:31.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,山姆\N{\rENG}Sam.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.38,0:23:32.23,CHS,,0,0,0,,你為啥要烏鴉嘴\N{\rENG}Why would you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.23,0:23:34.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,不是姐們 這你也能怪我啊\N{\rENG}What? Oh, come on, you can't blame me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.18,0:23:35.02,CHS,,0,0,0,,相位槍調到擊殺檔\N{\rENG}Phasers to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.34,0:23:36.93,CHS,,0,0,0,,該走了\N{\rENG}Time to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.12,0:23:44.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,我和烏乎拉一直在鑽研\N{\rENG}Uhura and I have been poring over
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.86,0:23:46.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,手頭能得到的戈恩人數據\N{\rENG}all available data on the Gorn.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.64,0:23:49.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,確認的襲擊 未被證實的目擊\N{\rENG}Confirmed attacks, unverified sightings.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.00,0:23:51.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,如果可能和戈恩人有關係 我們就檢查過一遍\N{\rENG}If it might be a Gorn, we've checked it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.72,0:23:53.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,比我們想像的信息多出很多\N{\rENG}And there's a lot more out there than we thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.22,0:23:56.52,CHS,,0,0,0,,你得稍微用點想像力\N{\rENG}You have to squint a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.52,0:23:57.95,CHS,,0,0,0,,但是每一次戈恩目擊事件\N{\rENG}But every Gorn sighting correlates
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.95,0:24:00.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,都和某個特定的恆星活動規律正相關\N{\rENG}to a pattern of specific stellar events.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.26,0:24:01.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,日冕物質拋射\N{\rENG}Coronal mass ejections.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.36,0:24:02.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,我已經了解過了\N{\rENG}I know this already, CMEs.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.96,0:24:04.66,CHS,,0,0,0,,恆星耀斑爆發會引發強烈恆星風\N{\rENG}Stellar flares can set off a frenzy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.66,0:24:06.61,CHS,,0,0,0,,是的 其活動遵循一定的規律\N{\rENG}Yes, the attacks follow a pattern,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.61,0:24:09.09,CHS,,0,0,0,,戈恩人的休眠也是如此\N{\rENG}but so does Gorn inactivity.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.27,0:24:11.27,CHS,,0,0,0,,這都是烏乎拉發現的\N{\rENG}Uhura is the one who found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.44,0:24:12.79,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們知道有很長一段時間\N{\rENG}There are long periods of time
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.79,0:24:14.67,CHS,,0,0,0,,沒有任何戈恩人活動的報告\N{\rENG}where no Gorn activity is reported.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.84,0:24:16.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,甚至連一點風聲都沒有\N{\rENG}Not so much as a rumor.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.45,0:24:18.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,在那個時間段\N{\rENG}And in those instances,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.23,0:24:21.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,獨特的恆星活動似乎觸發了某些東西\N{\rENG}there's unique stellar activity that seems to trigger...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.10,0:24:22.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,休眠\N{\rENG}Hibernation.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.00,0:24:22.89,CHS,,0,0,0,,沒錯\N{\rENG}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.89,0:24:25.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們認為戈恩人有著漫長的休眠週期\N{\rENG}We believe that the Gorn have a long hibernation cycle.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.16,0:24:27.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,在適當的條件下 它們會變得溫順\N{\rENG}Under the right conditions, they become docile.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.34,0:24:28.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們可以利用這一點\N{\rENG}We can use that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.18,0:24:29.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們的科學團隊協助了計算\N{\rENG}The science team chipped in on the math
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.90,0:24:32.42,CHS,,0,0,0,,成功識別出X級太陽耀斑及其伴隨的上弓下沉流\N{\rENG}and was able to isolate the presence of X-class flares
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.42,0:24:34.73,CHS,,0,0,0,,兩者在消失前均有明顯前兆\N{\rENG}and supra-arcade downflows that precede their absence.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.25,0:24:39.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,做的好 你們倆\N{\rENG}Good work, both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.08,0:24:40.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,還有一點\N{\rENG}There's something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.56,0:24:43.20,CHS,,0,0,0,,數據表明\N{\rENG}The data also suggests that
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.20,0:24:47.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們可能正處於戈恩人長期侵略行為的初期\N{\rENG}we could be at the beginning of a long cycle of Gorn aggression.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.26,0:24:49.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,這些襲擊可能預示著\N{\rENG}These attacks could signal what
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.58,0:24:52.57,CHS,,0,0,0,,戈恩人即將發動全面入侵\N{\rENG}could soon be a full-scale Gorn invasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.60,0:24:57.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,艦長 我們將在兩分鐘後脫離曲速\N{\rENG}Dropping out of warp in two minutes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.36,0:24:59.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,謝謝你 米歇爾 我們這就來\N{\rENG}Thank you, Mitchell. On our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.20,0:25:12.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,史波克和查普爾知道自己在做什麼\N{\rENG}Spock and Chapel know what they're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.12,0:25:13.96,CHS,,0,0,0,,我相信他們\N{\rENG}I trust them
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.96,0:25:15.81,CHS,,0,0,0,,會好好利用我的血液\N{\rENG}with a couple liters of my blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.08,0:25:19.12,CHS,,0,0,0,,謝謝你\N{\rENG}Thank you for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.25,0:25:21.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,他們說這可能是她唯一的機會\N{\rENG}They say it may be her only hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.08,0:25:23.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,為了瑪麗 他們需要什麼我都願意提供\N{\rENG}For Marie, they can take all they want.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.62,0:25:25.20,CHS,,0,0,0,,這次任務不留存記錄\N{\rENG}This mission's already off-the-record,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.20,0:25:26.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,所以也沒什麼好報告的\N{\rENG}so nothing to report.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.17,0:25:29.65,CHS,,0,0,0,,克里斯\N{\rENG}Chris,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.78,0:25:31.83,CHS,,0,0,0,,聽一聽你自己的建議吧\N{\rENG}take some of your own advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.00,0:25:34.09,CHS,,0,0,0,,要抱有希望\N{\rENG}Focus on hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.05,0:25:41.48,CHS,,0,0,0,,伊勒利亞血液供給方案已完成\N{\rENG}Illyrian blood donor scenario completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.48,0:25:45.19,CHS,,0,0,0,,死亡概率為86%\N{\rENG}Probability of fatality: 86%.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.67,0:25:47.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,只有這個方案能讓她有一線生機\N{\rENG}That's the first one that's given her any chance at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.70,0:25:49.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,雖然成功率也不高\N{\rENG}Albeit not a very high one.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.26,0:25:51.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,按理說 不能在這種概率下進行手術\N{\rENG}I mean, we can't do the surgery with these odds.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.40,0:25:54.85,CHS,,0,0,0,,但總算有所進展了 我們繼續努力\N{\rENG}We're on to something. Let's keep at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.34,0:25:56.48,CHS,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\rENG}Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.90,0:26:01.73,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們已接近輻射區\N{\rENG}We're near the radiation zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.73,0:26:03.99,CHS,,0,0,0,,從現在起 只能使用脈衝引擎\N{\rENG}From here on, it's impulse engines only.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.80,0:26:11.48,CHS,,0,0,0,,米歇爾 你連續工作很久了\N{\rENG}Mitchell, you've been running nonstop.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.48,0:26:12.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,去換班吧\N{\rENG}Call for relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.58,0:26:14.57,CHS,,0,0,0,,恕我直言 在把所有人都救回來前\N{\rENG}With respect, I'm not leaving the station
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.57,0:26:16.22,CHS,,0,0,0,,我絕不離開崗位\N{\rENG}until we get everyone back.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.53,0:26:18.75,CHS,,0,0,0,,明白了\N{\rENG}Copy.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.31,0:26:21.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,謝謝你\N{\rENG}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.67,0:26:28.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,我收到了沃凱礦的信號\N{\rENG}I have the wolkite signature.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.32,0:26:30.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,即將接近敵方驅逐艦\N{\rENG}We're coming up on the enemy destroyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.06,0:26:31.20,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們多久能追上他們\N{\rENG}How soon can we overtake them?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.20,0:26:32.46,CHS,,0,0,0,,克里斯 我們可能來晚了\N{\rENG}Chris, we may be too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.46,0:26:33.89,CHS,,0,0,0,,他們已經進入了輻射區\N{\rENG}They've already entered the radiation zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.89,0:26:35.84,CHS,,0,0,0,,如果我們繼續深入當前星系\N{\rENG}If we go any deeper into this star system,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.84,0:26:37.30,CHS,,0,0,0,,全體船員都將陷入危險\N{\rENG}we put the entire crew at risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.30,0:26:38.42,CHS,,0,0,0,,舵手 立即停船\N{\rENG}Helm, full stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.03,0:26:43.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,主屏幕切換為遠距離觀測畫面\N{\rENG}Put the long-range visual up on the main screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.43,0:26:49.25,CHS,,0,0,0,,是我的錯覺 還是\N{\rENG}Is it me, or does it look like
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.25,0:26:51.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,那艘船確實正朝著恆星的方向行駛?\N{\rENG}that ship is going to fly right into that star?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.18,0:26:54.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,我也看到了 簡直難以置信\N{\rENG}I see it, I don't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.88,0:26:57.39,CHS,,0,0,0,,遙測數據已確認 艦長\N{\rENG}Telemetry confirms, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.39,0:26:58.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們必須做點什麼\N{\rENG}We have to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.62,0:26:59.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,你看\N{\rENG}Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.22,0:27:03.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,他們是失去動力了嗎\N{\rENG}Did they just lose power?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.05,0:27:06.01,CHS,,0,0,0,,不是\N{\rENG}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.23,0:27:08.53,CHS,,0,0,0,,我認為他們是故意的\N{\rENG}I think it was intentional.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.53,0:27:10.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,但為什麼呢\N{\rENG}But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.86,0:27:19.50,CHS,,0,0,0,,將全部備用能量傳輸至護盾\N{\rENG}All auxiliary power to the shields.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.50,0:27:22.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,盡可能爭取在輻射區停留的時間\N{\rENG}Give me as much time as possible inside that radiation zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.06,0:27:24.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們追上去\N{\rENG}We're going after 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.25,0:27:32.65,CHS,,0,0,0,,新一輪日冕物質拋射活動逼近\N{\rENG}We've got another CME flare coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.50,0:27:40.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,她快不行了\N{\rENG}She's coding.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.70,0:27:41.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,戈恩幼體正在孵化\N{\rENG}The Gorn hatchlings are activating.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.46,0:27:44.20,CHS,,0,0,0,,有什麼東西加速了它們的生長\N{\rENG}Something has accelerated their growth.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.20,0:27:46.79,CHS,,0,0,0,,14%的成功率總比注定的死亡要好\N{\rENG}A 14% chance of survival is better than certain death.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.46,0:27:50.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,準備手術吧\N{\rENG}Let's prep her for surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.60,0:28:01.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,我還能接收到沃凱礦的信號\N{\rENG}I'm still getting a ping on the wolkite signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.38,0:28:03.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們必須盡我們所能拯救我們的船員\N{\rENG}We need to get to our people while we still can.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.02,0:28:07.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,這裡的磁場干擾讓導航系統無法運作\N{\rENG}The magnetic fields here make navigation impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.25,0:28:09.60,CHS,,0,0,0,,這就解釋了戈恩星艦為何會像失去動力一樣\N{\rENG}That explains why the Gorn go into a free fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.60,0:28:12.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,他們利用了強重力井來完成大部分機動\N{\rENG}They let the intense gravity wells do most of the work.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.69,0:28:14.47,CHS,,0,0,0,,星際艦隊方面沒有回覆\N{\rENG}No response from Starfleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.47,0:28:16.30,CHS,,0,0,0,,都是因為這些輻射\N{\rENG}It's all the radiation.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.30,0:28:17.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,無論是進取號還是雙星系統以外的區域\N{\rENG}And no visuals on the ship
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.88,0:28:20.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,都無法獲得影像反饋\N{\rENG}or what's beyond the binary stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.00,0:28:22.91,CHS,,0,0,0,,這種光線折射方式會生成一種自然全息投影\N{\rENG}The light bends in a way that creates a natural hologram.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.91,0:28:25.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,一旦穿過它 就無法被看到了\N{\rENG}They're essentially invisible once they pass through it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.31,0:28:27.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,形成了絕佳的防禦屏障\N{\rENG}Makes for a great defense system.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.18,0:28:29.01,CHS,,0,0,0,,也許那是一種降落程序\N{\rENG}Maybe it's a landing sequence.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.01,0:28:30.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,有沒有可能 戈恩母星就在這\N{\rENG}Could this be the Gorn homeworld?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.71,0:28:34.23,CHS,,0,0,0,,如果假設成立 那這就是他們回母星的方法\N{\rENG}If it is, that's how they go back to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.71,0:28:38.60,CHS,,0,0,0,,艦長\N{\rENG}Captain,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.60,0:28:39.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,外面有情況\N{\rENG}something's moving out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.90,0:28:40.60,CHS,,0,0,0,,屏顯\N{\rENG}On screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.36,0:28:55.49,CHS,,0,0,0,,一號\N{\rENG}Number One.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.17,0:29:05.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,我計算了他們的軌跡\N{\rENG}I've plotted their trajectory.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.72,0:29:07.83,CHS,,0,0,0,,那些艦船正徑直駛向聯邦領空\N{\rENG}Those ships are headed straight for Federation territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.83,0:29:08.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,警告星際艦隊\N{\rENG}Warn Starfleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.90,0:29:10.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,只能使用深空通訊中繼聯絡\N{\rENG}It's a deep space relay.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.44,0:29:12.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,我無法確實他們是否收到了訊息\N{\rENG}I won't be able to confirm if they receive it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.14,0:29:13.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們得走了\N{\rENG}We need to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.28,0:29:14.76,CHS,,0,0,0,,離開該星系的干擾範圍\N{\rENG}Get clear of this system's interference.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.76,0:29:16.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,艦長 如果我們現在失去沃凱礦的信號\N{\rENG}Captain, if we lose our lock on the wolkite signal,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.62,0:29:18.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,我無法保證我們能再次進行追蹤\N{\rENG}I'm not sure we can reestablish contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.64,0:29:20.76,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們會失去外勤小隊和殖民地居民\N{\rENG}We'll lose the landing party and the colonists.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.45,0:29:26.46,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們可以放置一個遠程通信浮標\N{\rENG}We can drop a long-range communication buoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.46,0:29:27.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,將信號連接到浮標上\N{\rENG}Tie a signal to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.98,0:29:29.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,這樣我們回來時就能找到他們了\N{\rENG}That way we can come back for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.63,0:29:32.37,CHS,,0,0,0,,這是我能想到的最好辦法了\N{\rENG}It's the best I've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.20,0:29:34.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,就這麼做\N{\rENG}Do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.40,0:29:36.99,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們必須阻止這場入侵\N{\rENG}We have to stop this invasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.26,0:29:38.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,通信浮標已部署\N{\rENG}Communication buoy is deployed.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.82,0:29:40.60,CHS,,0,0,0,,米歇爾 持續鎖定敵方艦隊\N{\rENG}Mitchell, stay on that enemy fleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.60,0:29:41.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,調轉艦艏\N{\rENG}Bringing her about.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.70,0:29:43.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,盡快曲速離開這裡\N{\rENG}As soon as we can, you warp out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.56,0:29:45.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,全速前進 直到我們能夠將警報發給星際艦隊\N{\rENG}Full throttle until we can alert Starfleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.30,0:29:49.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,現在我們是聯邦唯一的指望了\N{\rENG}We're the only hope the Federation's got right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.34,0:30:03.04,Note,,0,0,0,,* 此處查普爾和史波克穿的防護服與《原初系列》1x06 “The Naked Time” 中穿著的防護服是同一樣式
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.46,0:29:59.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,計算機 啟動隔離模式\N{\rENG}Computer, engage quarantine mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.30,0:30:02.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,隔離模式已啟動\N{\rENG}Quarantine mode engaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.98,0:30:20.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,如果失敗的話 這就是法雷奧貝塔的悲劇重演\N{\rENG}If this goes sideways, it's, it's Valeo Beta all over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.98,0:30:20.16,Note,,0,0,0,,* 見《奇異新世界》1x09 聯邦星艦遊隼號上爆發戈恩寄生疫情 墜毀在法雷奧貝塔五星
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.29,0:30:22.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,戈恩卵疫情在全艦爆發的可能性將會是\N{\rENG}The probability of a full-scale Gorn outbreak...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.73,0:30:24.69,CHS,,0,0,0,,我真的不想知道\N{\rENG}I really don't want to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.08,0:30:33.65,CHS,,0,0,0,,查普爾護士 聯邦星艦進取號\N{\rENG}Nurse Chapel, USS Enterprise...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.22,0:30:37.35,CHS,,0,0,0,,向患者巴特爾注射\N{\rENG}...injecting Patient Batel
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.35,0:30:40.09,CHS,,0,0,0,,實驗性血漿溶液\N{\rENG}with experimental plasma solution.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.04,0:30:47.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,有進展嗎 少尉\N{\rENG}Anything, Ensign?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.32,0:30:48.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,通訊仍受阻礙 艦長\N{\rENG}Still jammed, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.54,0:30:50.66,CHS,,0,0,0,,戈恩人正在發送干擾信號\N{\rENG}The Gorn are transmitting an interference signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.20,0:30:55.07,CHS,,0,0,0,,距我們離開雙星系統進入曲速還有多久\N{\rENG}How long before we clear these binary stars and go to warp?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.07,0:30:56.20,CHS,,0,0,0,,時間不夠\N{\rENG}Not soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.20,0:30:58.59,CHS,,0,0,0,,戈恩星艦的航速比我們快得多\N{\rENG}Those Gorn ships are moving a lot faster than we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.59,0:30:59.60,CHS,,0,0,0,,等警告發出\N{\rENG}By the time we get a signal out,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.60,0:31:01.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,戈恩艦隊已經到達聯邦外圍成員國的位置了\N{\rENG}the Gorn will be right on top of the outer Federation worlds.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.10,0:31:03.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,他們只能坐以待斃\N{\rENG}They're sitting ducks.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.94,0:31:06.12,CHS,,0,0,0,,米歇爾 我們在戈恩艦隊的武器射程內嗎\N{\rENG}Mitchell, are we in shooting distance of the Gorn?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.12,0:31:07.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,克里斯\N{\rENG}Chris,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.32,0:31:10.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,你要讓進取號對陣整個戈恩艦隊嗎\N{\rENG}Enterprise against an entire armada?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.36,0:31:12.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們根本不是對手\N{\rENG}We wouldn't stand a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.56,0:31:25.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,派克呼叫科學實驗室\N{\rENG}Pike to science lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.64,0:31:28.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,佩利亞 我需要你到艦橋來\N{\rENG}Pelia, I need you on the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.18,0:31:30.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,好的 艦長 馬上來\N{\rENG}Aye, Captain, right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.06,0:31:32.02,CHS,,0,0,0,,你打算做什麼\N{\rENG}What are you up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.50,0:31:35.67,CHS,,0,0,0,,你和烏乎拉\N{\rENG}You and Uhura,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.80,0:31:37.63,CHS,,0,0,0,,你們之前說恆星耀斑決定了\N{\rENG}you said stellar flares can dictate
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.76,0:31:40.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,戈恩人的狩獵和休眠週期\N{\rENG}a Gorn's hunting and resting cycles.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.46,0:31:41.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,確實如此\N{\rENG}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.86,0:31:43.77,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們甚至知道哪種輻射信號\N{\rENG}We even know precisely what kind of radiation signature
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.77,0:31:45.50,CHS,,0,0,0,,可以讓戈恩人陷入休眠\N{\rENG}would tell the Gorn to go to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.50,0:31:48.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,艦長 這只是理論上的\N{\rENG}Um, sir, that's just a theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.94,0:31:51.07,CHS,,0,0,0,,所以\N{\rENG}So...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.10,0:31:54.39,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們只需要人為製造一場恆星耀斑爆發\N{\rENG}...we just need to create a stellar flare.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.39,0:31:56.02,CHS,,0,0,0,,抱歉打斷您 艦長\N{\rENG}Oh, forgive me for interrupting,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.02,0:31:57.87,CHS,,0,0,0,,但我們基本沒辦法對恆星造成什麼影響\N{\rENG}but you cannot make a star do much of anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.00,0:31:59.80,CHS,,0,0,0,,更別說是精確控制耀斑爆發了\N{\rENG}Certainly not precisely, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.80,0:32:01.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,所以我們需要自己成為一次日冕物質拋射\N{\rENG}Which is why we need to become a CME, uh,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.09,0:32:03.39,CHS,,0,0,0,,也就是X級耀斑\N{\rENG}X-flare ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.27,0:32:06.24,CHS,,0,0,0,,艦長 你看\N{\rENG}Captain, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.24,0:32:07.48,CHS,,0,0,0,,抱歉 你介意騰位置嗎\N{\rENG}Uh, sorry, do you mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.96,0:32:09.30,CHS,,0,0,0,,嗯是 用星艦來操作\N{\rENG}Eh, sure, using the ship
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.30,0:32:12.50,CHS,,0,0,0,,的確能讓我們精準調控發射的輻射和電磁信號\N{\rENG}would allow us to modulate the exact radiation and EM signals we'd emit.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.50,0:32:14.41,CHS,,0,0,0,,但你說的基本上就是\N{\rENG}But you're basically talking about
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.41,0:32:16.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,把整艘船變成一顆人造恆星\N{\rENG}turning the ship into an artificial star.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.28,0:32:17.71,CHS,,0,0,0,,這基本上是不可能的\N{\rENG}That's-that's nearly impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.71,0:32:19.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,但並非完全不可能\N{\rENG}But not impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.06,0:32:21.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,為了達到這個目的 我們必須深入到\N{\rENG}To do that, we'd have to go deeper
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.34,0:32:23.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,這個致死的輻射區裡\N{\rENG}into this deadly radiation zone,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.66,0:32:25.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,徑直飛過外面那對雙星之間\N{\rENG}fly right between those binary stars out there,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.94,0:32:29.12,CHS,,0,0,0,,想辦法製造一個對抗磁場\N{\rENG}and create some kind of competing magnetic field
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.25,0:32:31.47,CHS,,0,0,0,,將粒子從雙星中引開\N{\rENG}to draw particles away from both of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.60,0:32:34.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,需要調整偏導護盾 通訊陣列 還有\N{\rENG}Modify the deflector shields, comms array, and, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.90,0:32:36.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,基本上系統都得重改一遍\N{\rENG}every-everything else, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.99,0:32:39.65,CHS,,0,0,0,,連艦體都要磁化 才能吸引恆星物質\N{\rENG}Magnetize the hull to attract stellar material.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.82,0:32:41.65,CHS,,0,0,0,,成功的機率是千分之一\N{\rENG}It's one in a thousand we'd get it done right
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.65,0:32:43.96,CHS,,0,0,0,,要麼能完成任務要麼炸飛自己 看吧\N{\rENG}or don't blow ourselves up along the way, and, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.96,0:32:50.05,CHS,,0,0,0,,我也不確定 但我願意賭一把\N{\rENG}Yeah, I don't know. I like those odds.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.88,0:32:53.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們就\N{\rENG}We'll just...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.14,0:32:55.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,在爆炸前把它關閉\N{\rENG}...turn it off before we blow up.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.80,0:33:01.19,CHS,,0,0,0,,就這麼辦\N{\rENG}Get it done.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.80,0:33:04.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,患者對輸血反應良好\N{\rENG}Patient is responding favorably to the transfusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.64,0:33:07.46,CHS,,0,0,0,,準備進行第一次手術切口\N{\rENG}Ready to make the first incision.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.36,0:33:42.66,CHS,,0,0,0,,等一下\N{\rENG}Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.85,0:33:50.07,CHS,,0,0,0,,你知道最壞的情況是巴特爾艦長會殉職\N{\rENG}You know the most likely outcome is the death of Captain Batel?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.07,0:33:52.76,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們只是需要一點信心\N{\rENG}We just have to have a little faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.76,0:33:55.55,CHS,,0,0,0,,或許我們是從錯誤的角度來看待這件事的\N{\rENG}Perhaps we are looking at this from the wrong perspective.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.44,0:33:58.12,CHS,,0,0,0,,與其在治療巴特爾上花時間\N{\rENG}Instead of operating on Batel,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.58,0:34:00.25,CHS,,0,0,0,,要是我們試著去對付一下戈恩人呢\N{\rENG}what if we treated the Gorn inside of her?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.18,0:34:02.40,CHS,,0,0,0,,它們想要孵化出來覓食\N{\rENG}We know they emerge to feed.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.40,0:34:03.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,要是我們給它們餵食呢\N{\rENG}What if we feed them?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.00,0:34:08.35,CHS,,0,0,0,,把它們餵飽 防止它們孵化\N{\rENG}Satiate them to keep them from coming out.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.52,0:34:11.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,當他們不再處於攻擊狀態時 把它們幹掉\N{\rENG}And when they are no longer in defensive mode, dissolve them.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.58,0:34:13.57,CHS,,0,0,0,,並用烏娜的伊勒利亞血漿\N{\rENG}And use Una's Illyrian plasma
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.57,0:34:15.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,來對抗他們在重新吸收過程中\N{\rENG}to fight the multitude of infections that will result
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.44,0:34:16.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,產生的大量感染\N{\rENG}from their reabsorption.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.72,0:34:17.42,CHS,,0,0,0,,沒錯\N{\rENG}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.36,0:34:21.84,CHS,,0,0,0,,但我們沒有時間再去模擬一次了\N{\rENG}But we don't have enough time to run another simulation.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.52,0:34:23.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,就像你剛才提議的那樣\N{\rENG}As you suggested,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.56,0:34:24.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,也許我們只是需要一點信心\N{\rENG}perhaps we just need a little faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.30,0:34:47.47,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們甩掉他們了嗎\N{\rENG}Did we lose them?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.47,0:34:49.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,或許吧\N{\rENG}Maybe,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.14,0:34:51.12,CHS,,0,0,0,,即便甩掉了 也是暫時的\N{\rENG}but if so, then not for long.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.13,0:34:54.66,CHS,,0,0,0,,這是個接口\N{\rENG}This is an interface.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.48,0:34:56.92,CHS,,0,0,0,,在戈恩的繁殖星球上\N{\rENG}They had them on the Gorn...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.92,0:34:58.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,也有這樣的裝置\N{\rENG}the Gorn breeding planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.84,0:35:02.74,CHS,,0,0,0,,我哥哥馬努 他\N{\rENG}My brother Manu, he...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.32,0:35:06.84,CHS,,0,0,0,,別害怕\N{\rENG}Don't be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.34,0:35:08.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,無論如何 別停下來\N{\rENG}Keep moving, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.98,0:35:09.74,CHS,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\rENG}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.30,0:35:15.80,CHS,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\rENG}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.20,0:35:18.59,CHS,,0,0,0,,你還好嗎\N{\rENG}Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.68,0:35:23.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,你現在在這裡 而不是在過去的那個地方\N{\rENG}You're here now, not back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.99,0:35:27.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,是啊 但這裡也沒好到哪去 不是嗎\N{\rENG}Yeah, but here's not great either, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.38,0:35:30.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,是啊 確實很糟糕\N{\rENG}No, I suppose not.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.24,0:35:38.46,CHS,,0,0,0,,我有印象了 讓我試試看\N{\rENG}I remember. Let me try something.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.32,0:36:02.80,CHS,,0,0,0,,太神奇了\N{\rENG}This is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.06,0:36:05.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,我很想把這個拆開 弄明白它是怎麼運作的\N{\rENG}I'd love to take this apart, figure out how it works.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.44,0:36:06.48,CHS,,0,0,0,,真是好主意\N{\rENG}Yeah, good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.48,0:36:07.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,在這待上一天慢慢研究吧\N{\rENG}Let's make a whole day of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.64,0:36:09.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,吃點零食 在這閒逛\N{\rENG}Get snacks, hang out.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.22,0:36:12.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,那些看起來像是緩衝信號\N{\rENG}Those look like buffer signatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.64,0:36:16.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,是的 還有傳送授權碼\N{\rENG}They are. And the transport codes.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.26,0:36:19.17,CHS,,0,0,0,,如果我們能把這個送回進取號\N{\rENG}If we can get this to the Enterprise,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.17,0:36:20.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,就能救走殖民地的居民\N{\rENG}then we can save the colonists.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.48,0:36:23.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,拯救所有人\N{\rENG}All of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.66,0:36:27.27,CHS,,0,0,0,,大伙們\N{\rENG}Guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.25,0:36:56.91,CHS,,0,0,0,,快去船上\N{\rENG}Get to the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.64,0:37:38.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們就位了\N{\rENG}We are in position,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.58,0:37:40.20,CHS,,0,0,0,,正在接近雙星\N{\rENG}approaching the binary stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.96,0:37:43.24,CHS,,0,0,0,,當我們關閉電磁脈衝發生器的瞬間\N{\rENG}The moment we shut down the EM emitter,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.24,0:37:46.22,CHS,,0,0,0,,每一艘戈恩星艦都會直奔我們而來\N{\rENG}every single Gorn ship is going to come at us.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.22,0:37:47.69,CHS,,0,0,0,,就像飛蛾撲火一樣\N{\rENG}Like moths to a flame.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.69,0:37:49.09,CHS,,0,0,0,,這也正是我們想要的效果\N{\rENG}Which is exactly what we want.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.06,0:37:52.96,CHS,,0,0,0,,大家準備好了嗎\N{\rENG}Everybody ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.53,0:38:02.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,像太陽一般閃耀吧\N{\rENG}Make us shine like the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.30,0:38:33.57,CHS,,0,0,0,,駕駛位\N{\rENG}The pilot seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.70,0:38:35.13,CHS,,0,0,0,,讓我坐駕駛位\N{\rENG}Put me in the pilot seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.26,0:38:36.22,CHS,,0,0,0,,我來駕駛它\N{\rENG}Put me in the pilot seat!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.40,0:38:37.57,CHS,,0,0,0,,別逞強了\N{\rENG}Forget about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.66,0:38:39.75,CHS,,0,0,0,,我能讓它飛起來 這非我不可\N{\rENG}I can fly it. It has to be me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.88,0:38:41.05,CHS,,0,0,0,,她說得對 我們必須得離開這\N{\rENG}She's right. We need to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.66,0:39:56.52,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們完全暴露在β粒子和伽馬射線中了\N{\rENG}We're covered in beta particles and gamma rays.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.52,0:39:58.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,星艦正在承受著臨界水平的輻射\N{\rENG}This ship is hitting critical levels of radiation!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.24,0:40:00.02,CHS,,0,0,0,,戈恩人在做什麼\N{\rENG}What are the Gorn doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.02,0:40:00.96,CHS,,0,0,0,,他們已經脫離編隊\N{\rENG}They have broken ranks,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.96,0:40:03.05,CHS,,0,0,0,,目前正處於進取號的攔截航線上\N{\rENG}currently on intercept course with Enterprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.05,0:40:04.48,CHS,,0,0,0,,目前看起來一切順利\N{\rENG}All right, so far, so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.48,0:40:05.35,CHS,,0,0,0,,現在看看它們會不會向我們開火\N{\rENG}Now let's see if they shoot at us.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.75,0:40:11.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,艦長 我收到了一個\N{\rENG}Captain, I have a signal bouncing off
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.19,0:40:12.49,CHS,,0,0,0,,通訊信標反射的信號\N{\rENG}the communications beacon.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.62,0:40:14.49,CHS,,0,0,0,,是拉安 長官\N{\rENG}It's La'An, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.45,0:40:18.42,CHS,,0,0,0,,進取號 能收到嗎\N{\rENG}Enterprise, are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.42,0:40:19.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,拉安 你在哪\N{\rENG}La'An, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.32,0:40:20.59,CHS,,0,0,0,,在路上 如果能收到信號的話\N{\rENG}On our way. If you can read me,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.59,0:40:22.20,CHS,,0,0,0,,注意接收我向你們發送的傳送密碼\N{\rENG}I'm sending you transport codes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.20,0:40:23.76,CHS,,0,0,0,,把帕納索斯人傳送出去\N{\rENG}Beam the Parnassians out.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.77,0:40:25.74,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們正在嘗試傳送\N{\rENG}We're trying to beam you out,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.74,0:40:26.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,但我們難以鎖定你們\N{\rENG}but we're having trouble getting a lock.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.12,0:40:28.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,你們收到了嗎\N{\rENG}Do you copy?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.62,0:40:30.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,它們正衝着我們來\N{\rENG}They're gaining on us!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.72,0:40:32.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,進取號 你們是否收到\N{\rENG}Enterprise, do you read me?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.08,0:40:33.21,CHS,,0,0,0,,把帕納索斯人傳送回艦\N{\rENG}Beam the Parnassians out.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.58,0:40:58.15,CHS,,0,0,0,,艦長 艦體完整性即將逼近極限\N{\rENG}Captain, hull integrity is approaching critical failure!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.90,0:41:13.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,把它關掉 關掉它\N{\rENG}Turn it off. Turn it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.78,0:41:22.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,起作用了嗎\N{\rENG}Did it work?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.35,0:41:26.39,CHS,,0,0,0,,沒錯 艦長 最後一艘戈恩船只已返回母星\N{\rENG}Aye, sir, the last of the Gorn have gone home.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.06,0:41:28.54,CHS,,0,0,0,,帕納索斯人呢\N{\rENG}What about the Parnassians?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.54,0:41:29.74,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們及時把他們傳回來了嗎\N{\rENG}Did we get them out in time?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.74,0:41:31.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,是的 艦長\N{\rENG}Yes, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.38,0:41:33.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,拉安的傳送密碼生效了\N{\rENG}The transport codes from La'An worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.62,0:41:35.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,幾百名殖民地居民已經被救回\N{\rENG}Several hundred colonists accounted for
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.32,0:41:37.19,CHS,,0,0,0,,正在送往應急醫務室\N{\rENG}and headed for the overflow infirmary.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.44,0:41:40.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,艦長 我們急需--\N{\rENG}Captain, we need immediate as--
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.18,0:41:42.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,將我們傳送上艦並讓一個醫療小組待命\N{\rENG}Beam us out and have a medical team standing by.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.64,0:41:46.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,派克呼叫輪機部\N{\rENG}Pike to Engineering?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.14,0:41:48.11,CHS,,0,0,0,,是 艦長 我們正在使用傳送碼\N{\rENG}Aye, Captain, we're using the transport codes
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.11,0:41:49.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,破解戈恩狩獵艦的系統\N{\rENG}to hack into the Gorn hunter,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.86,0:41:51.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,應該很快就能搞定\N{\rENG}should be just a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.64,0:41:54.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,克里斯 我們做到了\N{\rENG}Chris. Chris, we did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.73,0:41:57.60,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們引起了戈恩人的長時休眠\N{\rENG}We triggered a long hibernation in the Gorn.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.60,0:41:58.99,CHS,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\rENG}Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.70,0:42:00.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,但我忍不住在想\N{\rENG}But I can't help wondering
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.88,0:42:03.43,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們會不會只是把麻煩推給了未來的人們\N{\rENG}if we didn't just create a problem for someone else to solve later.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.04,0:42:08.65,CHS,,0,0,0,,艦長 我收到了艾普里爾上將的加密呼叫\N{\rENG}Captain. I'm getting a secure channel from Admiral April.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.65,0:42:09.83,CHS,,0,0,0,,接通\N{\rENG}Put him through.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.74,0:42:14.35,CHS,,0,0,0,,克里斯 我們剛收到你的優先級訊息\N{\rENG}Chris. We just got your priority message.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.35,0:42:16.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,在戈恩艦隊到這之前我們還有多少時間\N{\rENG}How much time do we have before the Gorn ships get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.38,0:42:17.83,CHS,,0,0,0,,請忽略最後一條訊息\N{\rENG}Ignore last transmission.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.83,0:42:19.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,至少在一段時間內我們見不著戈恩人\N{\rENG}We won't be seeing the Gorn, at least not for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.06,0:42:21.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,你有幾分把握\N{\rENG}How certain are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.82,0:42:23.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,怎麼說呢 我已經對戈恩人還以顏色了\N{\rENG}Let's just say I found a way to punch back.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.59,0:42:39.25,CHS,,0,0,0,,保持清醒 別暈過去\N{\rENG}Stay with me. Stay with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.80,0:42:44.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,我做的很棒\N{\rENG}I did good.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.69,0:42:45.73,CHS,,0,0,0,,不是嗎\N{\rENG}Didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.20,0:42:49.65,CHS,,0,0,0,,別說話了 你能撐住的\N{\rENG}Stop. You're going to make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.58,0:42:54.35,CHS,,0,0,0,,想幹掉我 他們還不夠格\N{\rENG}They'll have to try harder than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.39,0:42:59.27,CHS,,0,0,0,,我可是艾麗卡·奧特加斯\N{\rENG}I'm Erica Ortegas.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.27,0:43:00.96,CHS,,0,0,0,,無敵舵手\N{\rENG}I fly the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.16,0:43:02.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,撐住 有我在呢\N{\rENG}Hold on. I got you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.94,0:43:19.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們盡力了\N{\rENG}We did all we could.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.64,0:43:22.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,現在要看巴特爾艦長自己了\N{\rENG}It's in Captain Batel's hands now.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.47,0:43:24.73,CHS,,0,0,0,,的確\N{\rENG}Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.52,0:43:32.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,謝謝你\N{\rENG}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.82,0:43:36.09,CHS,,0,0,0,,沒有你的話 我沒法做到這一切\N{\rENG}I couldn't have done that without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.46,0:43:37.50,CHS,,0,0,0,,不用謝\N{\rENG}You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.97,0:43:54.67,CHS,,0,0,0,,她怎麼樣了\N{\rENG}How is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.67,0:43:56.45,CHS,,0,0,0,,她在實驗室裡 仍在恢復中\N{\rENG}She's in the lab, still in recovery.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.25,0:44:11.84,CHS,,0,0,0,,外勤隊已經救回\N{\rENG}Landing Party accounted for and
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.84,0:44:13.42,CHS,,0,0,0,,正在應急醫務室中接受治療\N{\rENG}getting treatment in the overflow infirmary.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.60,0:44:15.13,CHS,,0,0,0,,艾麗卡傷得很重\N{\rENG}Erica is critical...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.30,0:44:16.95,CHS,,0,0,0,,但目前穩定\N{\rENG}but stable.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.08,0:44:19.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,謝謝你的通知\N{\rENG}Thanks for the update.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.13,0:44:21.66,CHS,,0,0,0,,一旦我們離開輻射區域\N{\rENG}Once we clear the radiation bands,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.66,0:44:22.79,CHS,,0,0,0,,就設定航線回地球 曲速回家\N{\rENG}chart a course for Earth. Warp us home.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.87,0:44:25.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,遵命 一號完畢\N{\rENG}Of course. Number One out.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.56,0:44:56.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\rENG}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.82,0:44:59.13,CHS,,0,0,0,,好吧 主\N{\rENG}Okay, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.33,0:45:01.50,CHS,,0,0,0,,你贏了\N{\rENG}You win.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.36,0:45:11.97,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們\N{\rENG}Our Father,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.97,0:45:13.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,在天上的主\N{\rENG}who art in heaven...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.36,0:45:14.66,CHS,,0,0,0,,克里斯\N{\rENG}Chris?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.32,0:45:17.93,CHS,,0,0,0,,你醒了\N{\rENG}You're awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.78,0:45:21.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,是啊 我想這意味著\N{\rENG}Yeah. Which I assume means
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.10,0:45:24.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,那些小戈恩們還沒破肚而出\N{\rENG}that tiny Gorn didn't pop out of my body
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.00,0:45:25.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,殺了大家呢\N{\rENG}and kill everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.72,0:45:26.96,CHS,,0,0,0,,不\N{\rENG}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.52,0:45:30.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,當然沒有 我們都好好的呢\N{\rENG}No, no, no. We're still here.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.98,0:45:32.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,史波克和查普爾想出了治療方案\N{\rENG}Spock and Chapel came up with a treatment, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.94,0:45:35.95,CHS,,0,0,0,,我後面會讓他們解釋給你聽\N{\rENG}I'll have them walk you through it later, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.38,0:45:39.30,CHS,,0,0,0,,但你還沒有完全脫離危險\N{\rENG}...you're still not out of the woods yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.47,0:45:41.73,CHS,,0,0,0,,怎麼做到的\N{\rENG}How?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.74,0:45:45.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,烏娜幫的忙\N{\rENG}Una helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.00,0:45:48.61,CHS,,0,0,0,,克里斯 你就不應該那麼做\N{\rENG}Chris, you shouldn't have done that.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.61,0:45:51.69,CHS,,0,0,0,,瑪麗 我已經失去了太多 好嗎\N{\rENG}Marie, I've already lost too much, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.69,0:45:54.01,CHS,,0,0,0,,所以我們可以繼續爭\N{\rENG}So we can sit here and we can argue about
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.01,0:45:55.97,CHS,,0,0,0,,爭論未來會不會發生什麼\N{\rENG}what might or might not happen in the future,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.97,0:45:58.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,但能不能把那些都放一邊 讓我抱著你\N{\rENG}or you can just set all that aside and let me hold you.
